# Stability Progress Tracker

This extension adds goal adherence tracking and a monthly Stability Score to help caseworkers prioritize follow-up and allocate limited capacity effectively. The design maintains a strengths-based, non-punitive approach—the score measures system and applicant partnership health, not applicant "failure."

---

## Design Philosophy

| Principle | Rationale |
|---|---|
| **Shared Accountability** | Tracks both applicant *and* caseworker/system actions to avoid penalizing applicants for missed appointments the agency scheduled |
| **Strength-Based** | Rewards progress, not just compliance; documents wins alongside barriers |
| **Capacity-Aware** | Helps caseworkers see which cases need more outreach vs. which are self-sustaining |
| **Non-Punitive Display** | Score is hidden from applicants; used internally for resource triage only |

---

